Test Case 2 (Positive)
Preconditions: - user is logged in

1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/ -> page opened
2. Click on username from top right corner -> user details pop-up is displayed
3. Click "Выход" button -> user is redirected to login page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login

Test Case 3 (Negative)
1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login -> page opened
2. Enter invalid password (Student, 9090909) -> Entered
3. Click "Вход" button -> user is not logged in. http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login page is opened. Password field cleared
4. Repeat steps 2-3 for invalid Email(name) -> user is not logged in. http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login page is opened. Password field cleared

Test Case 4 (Positive)
Preconditions: - user is logged in

1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/ -> page opened
